"It was all Miley's idea to have as many bears as possible," Corey explained. "We had an illustrator and cartoonist design the faces of the bears, including those for the girls who were twerkers and 'Amazon Ashley,' who had the bear head on her back and was throwing out marshmallow treats into the audience. Those were designed by an artist named Todd 'REAS' James."
